{"tid":994922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報美軍救命之恩 英國老翁成功爭取檢閱飛行紀念儀式","createTime":"2019-01-25T05:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T06:00:32.000Z","uid":28765,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6388ab69c0f41be2219f3889b97eccb699478ea5","tid":994922,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190123/photo/bkn-20190123170026715-0123_00912_001_01p.jpg?20190123174229\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190123%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190123170026715-0123_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20190123174229&h=db35aef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n富爾德每天風雨不改前往打掃紀念碑。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n英國一名老翁於二戰時目睹一架美軍轟炸機失事，但機師在轟炸機着地前，盡最後努力避開公園的人群，最終10名機員身亡。他認為受了美軍的救命大恩，多年來一直打理紀念碑，並成功爭取美軍在下月22日，即轟炸機墜毀75周年時，派軍機飛越紀念碑上方，向當年殉職機員致敬。 <br />\n<br />\n事發於1944年2月22日，只有8歲的富爾德（Tony Foulds）在安德克里夫公園與朋友玩耍，期間一架名為「Mi Amigo」，剛完成轟炸任務的B17空中堡壘轟炸機返航時失控，墜毀在公園附近。富爾德直到十多歲時才明白，那是一場很可怕的意外。他說：「如果他們（美軍）沒有犧牲性命，我現在不能在這裏。」 <br />\n<br />\n政府1970年代在公園內豎立紀念碑，富爾德每天風雨不改地前往打掃及種花，並向這班恩人報告自己的生活情況及每日的天氣。他出國旅行時，亦會吩咐兒子代為打理紀念碑。直至本月初，富爾德於紀念碑附近遇到英國廣播公司（BBC）的節目主持沃克（Dan Walker），並把自己希望為恩人爭取檢閱飛行紀念儀式一事告訴他。沃克於是在社交網站發起行動，呼籲網民轉發。結果美國軍方迅速答應了富爾德的請求，屆時美軍及英軍戰機會飛越公園的上空。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190123/photo/bkn-20190123170026715-0123_00912_001_02p.jpg?20190123174229\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190123%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190123170026715-0123_00912_001_02p.jpg%3F20190123174229&h=832b07dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n富爾德實現願望後感到欣慰。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190123/mobile/bkn-20190123170026715-0123_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190123%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190123170026715-0123_00912_001.html&d=9P9Iq%2B49TWHZ5%2Bjigqrf1ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=d84b845a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190123/mobile/bkn-20190123170026715-0123_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2616a49618eb9885e6beaf409d33dc706b624004","tid":994922,"uid":59030,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:20:46.000Z","msg":"龍鼓灘都有部b25被日軍擊落<br />\n無人記念佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c7c2040172d7d1940836871007da10a21279e9","tid":994922,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2616a49618eb9885e6beaf409d33dc706b624004","tid":994922,"uid":59030,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:20:46.000Z","msg":"龍鼓灘都有部b25被日軍擊落<br />\n無人記念佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"你去日本叫架仔過黎上香<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71b61e37772b9853bf4ce52b5231ef19d96c163","tid":994922,"uid":89056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2616a49618eb9885e6beaf409d33dc706b624004","tid":994922,"uid":59030,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:20:46.000Z","msg":"龍鼓灘都有部b25被日軍擊落<br />\n無人記念佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:22:59.000Z","msg":"共匪點會做呢d野，重光記念日都冇左就知啦"},{"pid":"91061b0bf3709f4376e67b6b893ab05fd479d86c","tid":994922,"uid":59030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"22c7c2040172d7d1940836871007da10a21279e9","tid":994922,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2616a49618eb9885e6beaf409d33dc706b624004","tid":994922,"uid":59030,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:20:46.000Z","msg":"龍鼓灘都有部b25被日軍擊落<br />\n無人記念佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"你去日本叫架仔過黎上香<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:23:30.000Z","msg"